#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:6
msgid "Help | Wednesday Challenge"
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:11
msgid "Dear fellow puzzlers,"
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:12
msgid ""
"you certainly know that our Wednesday challenge is our special bonus over and"
" above the basic rules of the game itself. The player who wins the Monday "
"game, immediately after the winners are announced on Tuesday at 6 pm, is "
"authorized to determine three words, which are the basis of our Wednesday "
"challenge and which all willing players enter into the game and are awarded "
"points for it."
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:13
msgid ""
"Because we strive for your comfort as well as ours, we have created the "
"comfort of entering words directly into the system for you."
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:13
msgid "🤗"
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:14
msgid ""
"We take into account that you may not have the desire, courage or just the "
"time to devote yourself to this, so we have expanded the possibility of "
"registration to each Monday player, according to the time that has passed "
"since the winners were announced on Tuesday at 6 pm."
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:16
msgid "At 6 pm, the possibility of registration opens on the page"
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:16
msgid ""
"for the golden winner. Every 5 hours later, this option will open to everyone"
" else. So after 11:00 pm, you will be able to enter the words gold and "
"silver. From 4:00 am next day, bronze will also be added, and so on. If the "
"words have not been entered by Wednesday at 5:00 pm, the form will already be"
" open to all players who completed Monday's game. At 5:59 pm, even for "
"players with a lamp, but I'm telling you straight up, if I'm looking for "
"words on Wednesday at 5:00 pm, don't wish me, f*ck it!"
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:16
msgid "😠"
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:18
msgid ""
"After entering the words, they will appear on the website immediately and "
"anyone can immediately view them. I recommend that you all keep an eye on the"
" words in this way."
msgstr ""

#: lustitelskadb/templates/help/wednesday_challenge.xhtml:19
msgid ""
"If you have any problems, don't hesitate to contact any of us. We are nice "
"and helpful."
msgstr ""

